{
  "stem": "2620.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And then, anyway, then they took us-- they-- from everybody moved from their home into the ghetto, and we were there for a while.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Munkatsh, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was-- it's called the-- the Yiddish [NON-ENGLISH], which is the Jewish street.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so, we were all cramped in there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Into one street.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As far as I know, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know how-- I don't remember how far back it went or-- I just know we were just in-- in there and-- and then not too long after that, we all went to-- they all-- we marched through the city to a brick factory.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were there for a few days, I guess.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everybody-- all the Jews-- the whole--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--family, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and I guess the reason for that is because the-- the train came right through there, into the brick factory.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they-- from there, we were sent to Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From the-- from that-- from the ghetto to the brick factory.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, all in one room-- all in one room, yeah.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All in one room, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, to go back a little bit, you-- you mentioned that you left school because you wanted to dress nicely.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 141,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you were now-- so this was round about when you were 12, 13.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 143,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 144,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 145,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 145,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I didn't have enough courage.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I didn't feel-- I didn't feel that I was-- that I had enough money to take out girls.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I actually never had a date before-- before the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I-- I don't-- I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 150,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we took just whatever we could.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 151,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just-- just clothing-- just clothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 151,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't think we took any-- anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
